    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s been absolute gold to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape, super clean inside and out, and has clearly been well-loved over the years. Perfect for anyone looking for a reliable daily driver that still looks sharp on the road. I\u2019ve kept up with all the maintenance, so it\u2019s ready for its next adventure whenever you are! Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re gonna love how it handles!",
