    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for all your weekend adventures? I\u2019m parting with my trusty car, and it has been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in really solid shape, runs super smooth, and has clearly been well-loved over the years. It\u2019s the perfect fit for someone who wants a dependable, quality vehicle without the brand-new price tag. I'd love for it to go to a good home, so come take it for a spin\u2014I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll fall in love with it just like I did!",
