    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This naturally aspirated power plant features individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system, providing a sharp 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a factory variable M differential lock. Recent preventative maintenance includes reinforced rear subframe mounts and a valve clearance adjustment. The chassis remains taut with no bushing deflection, and the suspension geometry provides the precise turn-in these cars are known for. While the exterior shows honest wear consistent with a well-loved driver, the powertrain remains in peak operating condition for the enthusiast seeking an analog performance experience.",
